    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "A JSON string in an HTML `<script>` tag may cause the parser to enter the [script data double escaped state](http://www.w3.org/TR/html5/tokenization.html#script-data-double-escaped-state), in which `</script>` would not return the parser to the data state as expected.\n\nsample.html:\n\n``` html\n<!doctype html>\n<script>alert({{ v|tojson|safe }});</script>\n```\n\nsample.py:\n\n``` python\nreturn render_template('sample.html', v='<!--<script>')\n```\n"
